{"tid":2247534,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"哈薩克對脫疆者發難民證 意味承認再教育營存在","createTime":"2020-10-18T02:31:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T03:32:19.000Z","uid":21470,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0712b0cabe1458a6484da26ede74a3c8c9d80ff4","tid":2247534,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T02:31:40.000Z","msg":"哈薩克對脫疆者發難民證 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哈薩克人權組織表示，哈薩克政府對兩名逃離中國新疆的哈薩克族人簽發難民證，意味當局首次正式承認新疆存在再教育營。組織表示，兩名逃離新疆的哈薩克人，去年10月非法入境，之後被捕，其後提出難民庇護申請，日前獲批有效期一年的難民證，反映哈薩克政府首度以官方文件證實新疆存在再教育營。 <br />\n<br />\n兩名脫疆者曾表示，不堪中國當局多年折磨而被迫逃亡，又指遭到中國警方拘留後受到虐打，由於得知可能會再被捕，決定偷渡進入哈薩克尋求庇護。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2362117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2362117&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=fa451a9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2362117</a>"},{"pid":"a1882163faa5a400db9a9f17d726b60c952a723e","tid":2247534,"uid":218082,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T02:38:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cOHhQ8H.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcOHhQ8H.gif&h=b3123b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCz0OVo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCz0OVo.gif&h=7eeb887e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過支那國對住哈薩克都唔會夠膽發難,呢個賤種國家只會夠膽對付國內嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef73ec8c477952f5a2e63759b3be7a36d3efcc7","tid":2247534,"uid":140831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1882163faa5a400db9a9f17d726b60c952a723e","tid":2247534,"uid":218082,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T02:38:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cOHhQ8H.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi